channel.title: A MSCP sig I found
channel.description:
Respected: [code] Tonypker13 Known him for ages, stormcutter help me make my first server, all moderators and administrators of moparscape for making the Moparscape economy the best! [/code] And thank-you players for joining MoparScape!
1st person is banned, 2nd person is banned, 3rd people, I really don't know what to say. Also, what economy? WTF are we selling/buying? Under that, it says thank-you. Why did he need a hyphen to say thank you?
